#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:2
#: 843cb76f347048ec91848b9ccba348b4
msgid "安信可 GPS系列模块 FAQ"
msgstr "Ai-Thinker GPS Series Module FAQ"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:17
#: c01713d240e84219805fc9410654ff0d
msgid "GP-02出货配的天线是无源天线还是有源天线"
msgstr ""
"Is the antenna shipped with GP-02 a passive antenna or an active antenna?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:18
#: 7e3cb6f8a4ba4ac8a7d5a948b88c1096
msgid "无源天线"
msgstr "Passive antenna."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:21
#: 445f403f39a94d13ac7e67c6bfbadc9d
msgid "GP-02开发板上的圆形器件是什么？实际电路设计能否不接？型号是什么？"
msgstr ""
"What is the round component on the GP-02 development board? Can it be "
"omitted in the actual circuit design? What is its model?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:22
#: de42ff8b3ac64369ade8894df05962b6
msgid "圆形器件是法拉电容，不是纽扣电池，型号为XH414H。实际电路设计可以不接"
msgstr ""
"The round component is a Farad capacitor, not a coin cell battery. The model "
"is XH414H. It can be omitted in the actual circuit design."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:25
#: 315780bf956145c99c513dabf4f7a974
msgid "GP-01和GP-02有什么区别"
msgstr "What is the difference between GP-01 and GP-02?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:26
#: 04c7f08cc8ee40949c35740f67dd42df
msgid "只是封装不同，其他软件功能都一样"
msgstr "Only the package is different. Other software functions are the same."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:29
#: d9d17352ea634af282320e27327b66ca
msgid "GPS模组上的VCC_RF引脚是做什么用途使用"
msgstr "What is the VCC_RF pin on the GPS module used for?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:30
#: 46e0643e25f342e2a8c739b565064fe0
msgid "给有源天线引脚进行供电"
msgstr "It is used to supply power to the active antenna pin."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:33
#: 2dd371707ba04d71b24bf1608f55c857
msgid "GP-02和BG-02有什么区别"
msgstr "What is the difference between GP-02 and BG-02?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:34
#: 857fd06caea14d6a84703e267c881fea
msgid "芯片厂商不同"
msgstr "They use chips from different manufacturers."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:37
#: 194aa9686d4447529c3d162206cecfff
msgid "GP-01的串口有两个吗"
msgstr "Does GP-01 have two serial ports?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:38
#: 9634195dc2234575ba2d04608f40234c
msgid "没有两个，只有一个串口"
msgstr "No. It has only one serial port."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:41
#: 20a738ac7a854ba2b9340901422e713f
msgid "GPS上的VRTC引脚安装3V纽扣电池有没有起作用"
msgstr ""
"Does installing a 3V coin cell battery on the VRTC pin of the GPS module "
"work?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:42
#: 5524398ee2f84b9eaaabb3bb182a1925
msgid ""
"VBAT有供电会有热启动功能，如果VBAT有供电，GPS定位后断电，再次上电会有RTC时间"
"输出。"
msgstr ""
"If VBAT is powered, the module supports hot start. If VBAT is powered, after "
"the GPS obtains a a position fix and then powers off, RTC time will be "
"output when it is powered on again."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:45
#: 1213a925b1954569a44b6bdab3e7de2e
msgid ""
"GPS获取的时间能精确到ms的吗？，目前模块是1s返回一次时间，时间格式：hhmmss."
"sss，.sss这个显示是0，怎么设置才能看到值？"
msgstr ""
"Can the time obtained by GPS be accurate to milliseconds? Currently, the "
"module returns the time once per second. The time format is hhmmss.sss, but ."
"sss is displayed as 0. How can I set it to show a value?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:46
#: c75cf17c91bb42a3999172fa50429dbb
msgid "GPS都是按整秒输出的，不会有ms输出。"
msgstr "GPS outputs time in whole seconds and does not output milliseconds."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:49
#: 57838dc1e59849d58063a633ac3f7a6c
msgid ""
"如果GPS模块由于外界地理环境的原因，暂时收不到数据，你们的GPS模块是否仍然可以"
"送GPS本地的时间给MCU"
msgstr ""
"If the GPS module temporarily cannot receive data due to the external "
"geographical environment, can your GPS module still send the GPS local time "
"to the MCU?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:50
#: c062b3ff0d804e9c9d11c8c6ea9f800c
msgid ""
"GPS从定位到不定位时，模块仍然有时间输出，如果模块没有定位过是没有时间的。"
msgstr ""
"When the GPS module changes from a positioned state to a non-positioned "
"state, it will still output time. If the module has never been positioned "
"before, there will be no time output."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:53
#: aa528f371a654d7fa7e738b22be6fa48
msgid "GP-02模组能否使用GK9501指令集"
msgstr "Can the GP-02 module use the GK9501 command set?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:54
#: 739c91566d154ba095814e340f0752d8
msgid "不可以，两者芯片方案不同，不能兼容使用"
msgstr ""
"No. The two modules use different chip solutions and are not compatible."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:57
#: 42bcdbe242164fe1a2e3376d47542d34
msgid "GPS模块无法定位该如何排查"
msgstr ""
"How should I troubleshoot if the GPS module cannot complete positioning?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:58
#: 1b47d9484cad4a198678d755a0a8d893
msgid ""
"首先检查是否在室外测试，室内肯定无法定位的，其次检查下供电，一般使用3.3V"
msgstr ""
"First, check whether the test is being performed outdoors. Positioning is "
"definitely not possible indoors. Second, check the power supply. Generally, "
"3.3V is used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:61
#: c7e8fd6ea96940619c47d44e36581148
msgid "GPS模块是主动发送定位信息的吗"
msgstr "Does the GPS module actively send positioning information?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:62
#: 0d7ecc59e3384550b4d5e315cd1ffdfb
msgid "是的"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:65
#: b886be5d51db45afbdf08ef2529c4234
msgid "请问GP-01模组串口通信协议是哪一种协议？"
msgstr "What serial communication protocol does the GP-01 module use?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:66
#: 60c5c2c18f1b44bc8b4686ab5353e280
msgid "NMEA协议，下载该资源（），其中包含协议文档；"
msgstr ""
"NMEA protocol. Download this resource (), which contains the protocol "
"document."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:70
#: f927c170d02b46bda223c2a8c088b7db
msgid "GP-02能外接GPRS模块或者4G模块传递消息吗"
msgstr ""
"Can GP-02 be connected to a GPRS module or 4G module to transmit messages?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:71
#: 2b3e34f200724eac8ee07028f6024e95
msgid "可以外接，通过串口的方式"
msgstr "Yes. It can be connected externally via the serial port."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:74
#: 9a3c93971c164796a61fcb42eba9f6e1
msgid "GP-02模块可以导引无人机飞行吗"
msgstr "Can the GP-02 module guide a drone to fly?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:75
#: 9ad6f451fd7e4c73b8c71f1837ea1c16
msgid "模块不支持导引功能"
msgstr "The module does not support guidance functions."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:78
#: 0e269b458ce44944bfa683ebfb6ff5f2
msgid "GPS模组可以获取网络时间吗"
msgstr "Can the GPS module obtain network time?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:79
#: 6ca5289dab2f4cd6994065503c04bde5
msgid "不可以，不过可以通过搜星的方式获取UTC时间，然后自行转换"
msgstr ""
"No. However, it can obtain UTC time by searching for satellites, and then "
"you can convert it yourself."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:82
#: 47d7552351b846cf9a41c7781db21365
msgid "GPS模组只能使用有源天线吗"
msgstr "Can the GPS module only use an active antenna?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:83
#: fed2a2f8a9e34b4e81dd3add22ee5b51
msgid "有源天线和无源天线都可以使用"
msgstr "Both active antennas and passive antennas can be used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:86
#: 3792bb53b7e9470285e77fe915f3f0f5
msgid "GP-02开发板天线是有源天线还是无源天线，板子上用的电池还是电容"
msgstr ""
"Is the antenna on the GP-02 development board an active antenna or a passive "
"antenna? Is the component on the board a battery or a capacitor?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:87
#: 5aab00683d5d4e83863c99547d8a51c5
msgid "天线是无源天线，板子上使用的是超级电容"
msgstr "The antenna is a passive antenna, and the board uses a supercapacitor."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:90
#: a63ab9e05464462f92c4a2a5290ad2d0
msgid "GP-02开发板上的超级电容能保存参数大概多少个小时"
msgstr ""
"How many hours can the supercapacitor on the GP-02 development board save "
"parameters?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:91
#: 07174ea1b4054196809ee56cc5566022
msgid "这个需要实际测试，如果是一直开启定位测试的情况下建议经常供电使用"
msgstr ""
"This needs to be tested in practice. If positioning tests are continuously "
"enabled, it is recommended to power the module frequently."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:94
#: 0dd7203c9a44405c9a32e328e3a81aa3
msgid "请问GP-01模组的PPS信号有什么作用？"
msgstr "What is the function of the PPS signal on the GP-01 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/GPS/GP/index.rst:95
#: 09e9d0d4b499487e87d01260d973f039
msgid "信号为时间脉冲，用于时间同步。"
msgstr "The signal is a time pulse used for time synchronization."
